These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, prague, hannover, colone
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, superhero, sports, family
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
5. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| City   | boston | prague | colone | hannover |
| Movie-Genre        | action | superhero   | family | sports    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, rose, iris
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, soccer, skiing, sailing
1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Flower   | rose | balloon-flower  | azalea  | iris |
| Sport   | sailing    | swimming | skiing | soccer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, weightlifting, water-polo, climbing
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, poker, go
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4
3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
4. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | climbing | water-polo | weightlifting    | cricket      |
| Game   | poker        | go     | bridge | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, designer, firefighter, paramedic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, 7up, soy-milk
1. the designer is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
2. the paramedic is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the software-developer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Job         | paramedic | software-developer | designer | firefighter |
| Beverage   | 7up       | tea   | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, swimming, lacrosse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, april, may
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | surfing  | rowing    | swimming   | lacrosse       |
| Birthday   | august | may | april | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, almond-milk, milk
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, go, monopoly
1. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk      | mirinda | milk | sprite |
| Game   | monopoly | snooker     | poker  | go  |

