.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo, bolivar, cain
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, indian, brazilian, nigerian
1. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
2. the brazilian is on the left of the italian##1
3. the cain-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the nigerian is the bongani-smoker##1
5. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the indian is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | bongani | cain | bolivar | tiparillo    |
| Nationality     | nigerian | brazilian  | italian     | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
House: ranch-style, craftsman, wooden, farmhouse
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game, cain, vegafina
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
2. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the ranch-style house is between the farmhouse house and the craftsman house##2
6. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
7. the game-smoker is between the ranch-style house and the cain-smoker##2
8. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| House   | craftsman | ranch-style      | farmhouse | wooden |
| Cigar   | prince  | vegafina | game    | cain            |

