.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, green, red, apricot
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, may, march, august
1. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
2. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who likes red##2
4. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
5. the person who likes red is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | apricot | green   | purple | red |
| Birthday    | august     | may | december     | march  |

