.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, superhero, disaster, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, polish, french, american
1. the person watching satire movies is the american##1
2. the nigerian is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the american is between the nigerian and the person watching disaster movies##2
4. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
5. the american is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre      | superhero       | disaster   | satire | documentary |
| Nationality   | french | polish | american        | nigerian    |

