.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, r&b, gospel, soul
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, magic-tricks, camping, soul-polo
1. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the fan of pop##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is soul-polo##1
4. the person who's hobby is soul-polo is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | soul   | r&b      | gospel      |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | camping | soul-polo | singing |

