.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, musical, family, documentary
There are 4 different favourite beverages: documentaryade, iced-tea, sprite, milk
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking documentaryade##1
2. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching family movies is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | documentary | musical  | family  | martial-arts |
| Beverage   | milk  | sprite | documentaryade | iced-tea   |

