.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
City: san-francisco, new-york, liverpool, nizza
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, singing, camping, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| City   | liverpool | nizza | san-francisco | new-york |
| Hobby           | filmmaking     | skydiving     | camping   | singing         |

