.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, juice, sprite
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia, amaryllis, lily
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who growsazalea and the person drinking water##2
2. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who growslily##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking water##1
5. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | sprite | water         | iced-tea   | juice |
| Flower   | amaryllis    | zinnia | lily | azalea   |

