.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, chaman, aristoff, oliveros
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, techno, metal, dubstep
1. the fan of dubstep is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the fan of metal is the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the fan of techno is the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
5. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Cigar   | chaman | alhambra | aristoff    | oliveros |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | metal  | dubstep | techno     |

