.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
House: cottage, townhouse, ranch-style, cape-cod
City: paris, venice, rome, nizza
1. the ranch-style house is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to venice is the ranch-style house##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
5. the person traveling to venice is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to rome##2
6. the townhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| House         | cape-cod   | ranch-style | cottage | townhouse    |
| City   | rome | venice  | nizza     | paris |

