.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, d&b, funk
House: art-deco, tower, victorian, craftsman
1. the tower house is on the far left##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
3. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the victorian house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the fan of country##1
6. the victorian house is in an even position##4
7. the art-deco house is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | country    | d&b       | metal |
| House       | tower  | victorian | craftsman | art-deco  |

