.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola, fanta, lemonade
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, martial-arts, satire, musical
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | cola | fanta | mirinda  | lemonade |
| Movie-Genre     | disaster      | satire       | martial-arts | musical     |

