.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, disaster, sports, drama
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, tennis, handball, rugby
1. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person watching animation movies and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | sports   | drama | disaster |
| Sport   | rugby          | tennis | volleyball         | handball  |

 